          "settings": {
            "question": "Do I need to be spiritual to wear your jewelry?",
            "answer": "<p>Not at all. You don't need any experience, background, or even a belief system. You just need to notice what you're drawn to, that pull is your starting point. Everything else unfolds from there.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question-2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How do I know which piece is for me?",
            "answer": "<p><strong>You don't choose the piece, the piece chooses you. </strong></p><p>Browse slowly without overthinking. The one that keeps pulling your attention, the one you keep coming back to — that's the one. Your intuition already knows. Trust it.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_imK9x9": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What makes your jewelry different from other crystal jewelry?",
            "answer": "<p>Every piece is intentionally activated — each crystal, color, and design carries a specific energy chosen to awaken something in the person it's meant for. </p><p>This isn't decoration. </p><p>It's a daily tool for reconnecting with yourself. The piece you're drawn to holds codes your soul already recognizes, even when your mind doesn't know why.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hUzPAb": {
