          "settings": {
            "question": "How do you select your crystals?",
            "answer": "<p>Every crystal is chosen intuitively from where ever I am, I let them come to me. I have a great sense of selecting only the ones I can feel are carrying a high vibrations and are ready to work. </p><p>All crystals are 100% natural with no dyes, treatments, or enhancements of any kind. What you receive is pure, as it came from the earth.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_CrP7LY": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "What does it mean if my piece breaks?",
            "answer": "<p>In this work, a piece breaking isn't always an accident — it can mean the crystal has completed its purpose with you.</p><p>It absorbed what it needed to, held what it needed to hold, and its work is done.</p><p> If this happens, take a moment to acknowledge what that piece carried for you. It served you well. When you feel ready, something new will call to you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_hU9q9K": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I request a custom piece?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. If you feel called to something created specifically for you — a specific intention, crystal, or energy — custom pieces are available. </p><p>Reach out directly or visit the \"custom sacred ally\" page on my website and we'll co-create something made for exactly where you are right now.</p>"
