            "answer": "<p>We begin with breathwork, grounding exercises, and a live crystal sound bath — all designed to bring your body and mind into a state of deep stillness. </p><p>From this place of stillness, you're able to connect with your own soul and higher self to receive whatever you need most — healing, guidance, clarity.</p><p> Every session is different because every soul is different. People leave feeling grounded, clear, and like themselves again — sometimes more than they ever have.</p>"
          }
        },
